{"title":"ACTF2023CTFer simulator","uid":"4a92eb65476673f7a6c5f24417ab71f4","slug":"ACTF2023CTFer simulator","date":"2023-11-23T04:53:00.988Z","updated":"2023-11-23T04:53:00.990Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ACTF2023CTFer simulator.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<p>访问service并抓包</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/84TvBuenmgMbykRk.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>一直放包直到看到events.yaml，发送到重发器</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/vmIq35Cni0YS2BD6.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>得到200的状态码时拦截回包，这时候就可以进行修改配置文件的操作了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/l7GflpSldtVqqIsw.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>全局搜索，将100的energy全改成10000放包</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/IcIRL9m3Bz000BJk.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>修改成功后就可以玩游戏操作了，游戏有几个注意点</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.时间只有两天，第三天9:00时必须拿到8个flag</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.第一天会有考试，需要复习通过考试</span><br><span class=\"line\">3.失败了不要死磕，换种方法</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>当然也有小tips：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.可以在考试前两个小时开始复习（一定的pass机率不过成功率蛮高）</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.在打exp时最后还有inside在手上（越到后面inside越难拿）</span><br><span class=\"line\">3.wrong flag尽量改对</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在第三天9:00之前拿到至少8个flag之后进行抓包，当跳转回重新开始的页面时会有一次交互，截取数据包之后发送就能看到flag了<br><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/71vcXZHYuNSJUji0.png!thumbnail\" title=\"fig:\"></p>\n","text":"访问service并抓包 一直放包直到看到events.yaml，发送到重发器 得到200的状态码时拦截回包，这时候就可以进行修